      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Residual convergence to 1e-5 for all transport equations.",
      "rationale": "Not assessed at MRL 2. Solver residuals monitored and convergence confirmed at 1e-5 as standard practice, but formal uncertainty quantification of solver error not required at this risk level."
    },
    {
