      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD model input parameters must be shown to be equivalent to those used in the validation experiments.",
      "rationale": "Not assessed at MRL 2. Equivalency reviewed qualitatively; fluid properties and boundary conditions judged consistent between simulation and experiment based on engineering judgment."
